The paper deals with retrieving 3D models from 2D sketches, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for learning features falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach that outperforms state of the art methods, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research.
